products.title: Harriet Vintage Roman Blind
products.description: Harriet, a beautiful bird themed pattern bursting with colour at a great price. This multicoloured roman blind is perfect to add a bird theme to any room in your home, the array of colours in the pattern means it will fit in with most decor. Product id: db-rom0741 fabric colour: vintage material: 100% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining headrail: durable white headrail with top or face fix brackets.
